            <title>OPPO Reno 13 系列搭载自研抢网芯片 X1，宣称“一格信号流畅玩”</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/812/131.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/812/131.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
